reg_info.act_under: Registry Act   Loi sur l’enregistrement des actes

content.content: 1. A certificate of discharge under subsection 56 (1), section 62, subsection 65 (2) or section 66 of the Act shall be in Form 3 of Regulation 688 of the Revised Regulations of Ontario, 1990. O. Reg. 22/99, s. 1.
